  "1794830": {
    "name": "Macabre",
    "steam_appid": 1794830,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1794830/extras/e37d77875237e9103671eb64b94aa819.poster.avif?t=1766118085\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1794830/extras/e37d77875237e9103671eb64b94aa819.webm?t=1766118085\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1794830/extras/e37d77875237e9103671eb64b94aa819.mp4?t=1766118085\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>《异度惊魂》</strong> 是一款 <strong>高风险合作撤离恐怖游戏</strong>，在这里 <strong>潜行就是生存</strong>，而每一次裂隙都绝不相同。</p><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>地图在变化，目标在改变，异度者在学习。</strong> 在裂隙彻底崩溃之前，搜集稀有资源并努力稳定它，同时压制内心的恐惧。</p><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>生存从未被保证。</strong> 你可以选择与队友一起逃脱，也可以抛弃他们独自求生。<strong>信任脆弱，背叛容易。</strong></p><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >唯一不变的真相是… <strong>这就是《异度惊魂》。</strong></p><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1794830/extras/bea819f8a668d46636597c8c69bafe3f.poster.avif?t=1766118085\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1794830/extras/bea819f8a668d46636597c8c69bafe3f.webm?t=1766118085\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1794830/extras/bea819f8a668d46636597c8c69bafe3f.mp4?t=1766118085\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1794830/extras/00fd497fe1e53362befd597d382232d9.avif?t=1766118085\" width=780 height=1196 /></span></p><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1794830/extras/8a0a7be05568d517e28d78217eb9379b.avif?t=1766118085\" width=780 height=113 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1794830/extras/3a337482679de859684e10a9957054b5.avif?t=1766118085\" width=780 height=123 /></span></p><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1794830/extras/2d15a23a61c0a2bada2f37a7f116189a.avif?t=1766118085\" width=780 height=219 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1794830/extras/2dc9ec7394b15e77559965de28583941.avif?t=1766118085\" width=780 height=219 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1794830/extras/2535c5a2b86bcd09d4f03f98fad3ad9b.avif?t=1766118085\" width=780 height=219 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1794830/extras/9e299ea86f05fbb208569e776f00d09c.avif?t=1766118085\" width=780 height=219 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1794830/extras/6850638dd3e3d444dfb0abb5797161e7.avif?t=1766118085\" width=780 height=158 /></span></p><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1794830/extras/1ff0ae18349275ad6164043cb5b86be1.avif?t=1766118085\" width=780 height=393 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这里，你无法用枪火摆脱噩梦。<strong>《异度惊魂》</strong> 讲究的是潜行、智慧与冷静。你们必须紧密合作才能生存，或是背叛队友以独吞战利品。</p><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>请记住：异度惊魂捕猎的，正是那些偏离队伍的人。</strong></p><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1794830/extras/287142785b8a34f6e6116bb15c993ad4.poster.avif?t=1766118085\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1794830/extras/287142785b8a34f6e6116bb15c993ad4.webm?t=1766118085\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1794830/extras/287142785b8a34f6e6116bb15c993ad4.mp4?t=1766118085\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1794830/extras/16f65c6b39fd366bcae08c8e17401fef.avif?t=1766118085\" width=780 height=526 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >幸运的是，你会遇到 Banjo，这位古怪的幸存者痴迷于裂隙探索。他将用知识和装备指引你前进，是你的生命线，提供关键器材和升级，让你拥有一线生机。<strong>合理使用你的资源。</strong></p><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1794830/extras/7c2d0453ab9e2109a40ccf63f425123f.poster.avif?t=1766118085\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1794830/extras/7c2d0453ab9e2109a40ccf63f425123f.webm?t=1766118085\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1794830/extras/7c2d0453ab9e2109a40ccf63f425123f.mp4?t=1766118085\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1794830/extras/b89f31fff61553b0010c1580fbeba8f9.avif?t=1766118085\" width=780 height=484 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>异度惊魂会在你游玩时学习。</strong> <strong>依赖相同的手段，它就会适应。</strong> 每一次遭遇都迫使你即兴应变。干扰、眩晕，甚至牺牲，或许是唯一的出路。</p><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1794830/extras/9d3a80c49e4a50af0f8066f9e13dcb9d.poster.avif?t=1766118085\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1794830/extras/9d3a80c49e4a50af0f8066f9e13dcb9d.webm?t=1766118085\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1794830/extras/9d3a80c49e4a50af0f8066f9e13dcb9d.mp4?t=1766118085\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1794830/extras/1f424be2d0de235b7f84eda0cc9aaa02.avif?t=1766118085\" width=780 height=438 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每一次行动都是一场赌博。想要保住搜刮到的资源，<strong>你必须活着抵达撤离点。若是死亡，你将失去一切。</strong> 裂隙不会原谅错误，你的队友也不会。贪婪、犹豫或背叛，都可能和异度者一样致命。</p><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1794830/extras/12f8b33fddd84137299982cc8156bb83.poster.avif?t=1766118085\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1794830/extras/12f8b33fddd84137299982cc8156bb83.webm?t=1766118085\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1794830/extras/12f8b33fddd84137299982cc8156bb83.mp4?t=1766118085\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1794830/extras/455be15f8b6e20e7c9e9176cb77e0ae8.avif?t=1766118085\" width=782 height=473 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在躲避异度者的同时，你会在破碎的时空中搜集强大的 <strong>时空碎片</strong> 与奇异物品。每一件战利品都至关重要。合适的装备可以揭示隐藏的真相，干扰异度者，或助你坚持到最后的逃脱。</p><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1794830/extras/2a18c842f0981d43809f4fca1a759257.poster.avif?t=1766118085\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1794830/extras/2a18c842f0981d43809f4fca1a759257.webm?t=1766118085\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1794830/extras/2a18c842f0981d43809f4fca1a759257.mp4?t=1766118085\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1794830/extras/91e6f5240ef05e0402f4ca060c31e002.avif?t=1766118085\" width=780 height=452 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>没有两次行动是相同的。</strong> 每一个裂隙都会重新组合 <strong>随机的地图布局、不断变化的目标以及不可预测的异度者行为</strong>。无论进入多少次，你都不会真正感到安全。</p><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1794830/extras/b05f509588891f6b179e9b32fa5613ec.poster.avif?t=1766118085\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1794830/extras/b05f509588891f6b179e9b32fa5613ec.webm?t=1766118085\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1794830/extras/b05f509588891f6b179e9b32fa5613ec.mp4?t=1766118085\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1794830/extras/6e6057b937e474581023506ac8a3ceeb.avif?t=1766118085\" width=780 height=114 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>《异度惊魂》</strong> 由悉尼的独立团队 Weforge Studio 打造，我们专注于恐怖与多人游戏体验。我们的目标是在 Steam 上呈现最具沉浸感的多人恐怖体验。抢先体验是第一步，销售收入将持续投入开发。我们计划在未来加入新地图、新的异度者、新的谜题和章节，并根据玩家反馈不断完善。</p><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>《异度惊魂》</strong> 的设计灵感来自多年的游戏积累。自适应 AI 传承了《异形：隔离》的紧张氛围；撤离玩法的风险与收益循环借鉴了《猎杀：对决》和《逃离塔科夫》的强度；而信任、背叛与混乱合作的社交体验，则受到《DayZ》《恐惧症》和《饥荒》的启发。</p><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >归根结底，<strong>《异度惊魂》</strong> 讲述的是人与人的故事。游戏内语音聊天将创造出难以预料的联盟、对立与背叛。正如我们的联合创始人 Jay 和 Jake，当年在《DayZ》的语音频道中相识，我们希望玩家间的联结同样真实。</p><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1794830/extras/3c2abf032671a045f96ab144c10593e5.avif?t=1766118085\" width=780 height=166 /></span></p>",
